{"tid":993045,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"作品未完成先發瘋！女藝術家被「亞當人像」毒害15年，確診腦受損","createTime":"2019-01-23T15:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T16:00:04.000Z","uid":212399,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dee350adb3823d36ac1520c51d6b1bc2fd5abc3e","tid":993045,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:15:42.000Z","msg":"人類對地球的汙染日益嚴重，或許有一天，我們都將自食惡果...<br />\n加拿大有位女藝術家，名為Gillian Genser，這15年來，她的最新力作是一尊名為「亞當」的雕塑作品。Gillian到海邊收集貝殼、珊瑚、乾枯木頭、動物骸骨&hellip;等天然材料，經由敲打、打磨成適當的形狀和大小，再融合成雕像的一部分，漸漸雕塑出「亞當」人像。<br />\n「我每天花12個小時一個個打磨這些貝殼，再把它們組合在一起，一件件融入『亞當』的身體。」Gillian這樣說。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.fatonews.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/2-1.jpg?w=799\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.fatonews.com.br%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F2-1.jpg%3Fw%3D799&h=cae24cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然而，在創作過程中，Gillian彷彿受到詛咒般身體不適，每當她近距離對視亞當，和自己的作品處在同一個空間，她就會感到頭暈目眩、嘔吐、全身肌肉痠痛，症狀一天比一天嚴重，到了最後，Gillian甚至出現癡呆症狀，她還會不自覺地走上街頭閒晃，感到憂鬱焦躁、想自殺，也常自言自語。<br />\nGillian痛苦地覺得自己快要死掉了，但是她不想放棄創作，她想把作品完成。Gillian曾看過各種醫生，精神科、風濕病、內分泌科&hellip;她都就診過，但醫生們都找不出病因。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dxb5iEFW0AAF61c?format=jpg&amp;name=900x900\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDxb5iEFW0AAF61c%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D900x900&h=5f19ffc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n直到2015年，Gillian被診斷為重金屬中毒，醫生發現Gillian體內有高含量的鉛。<br />\n原來，Gillian收集而來的貝類，都來自於加拿大大西洋沿岸，當地是重金屬汙染區，貝類含有高含量的重金屬汙染物，當Gillian打磨貝類時，吸進了大量重金屬粉塵，因而中毒不適。但為時已晚，Gillian已患有嚴重的腦損傷，現在她必須在一個透明的隔離箱裡打磨貝殼才行。<br />\n寫到此，不禁感嘆，人類造成的汙染，終究會回到我們身上呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/41281\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F41281&d=SNcgiO0Jsq9L6NEwCudGKePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=0f7eda98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/41281</a>"},{"pid":"83b64abade38a69424d1da4a8ff9cd8c5f93f267","tid":993045,"uid":71913,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:16:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b349f7284e0026bf76c38053aa173ef250a3f5","tid":993045,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742d9631f2f12f85a3b03aba909bdea278623208","tid":993045,"uid":212399,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:18:24.000Z","msg":"以為係靈異野，點知唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d1062b0ae28f86a10dd3af5eaf7316c2a1e968","tid":993045,"uid":132587,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:19:11.000Z","msg":"台灣d media真係好戇鳩<br />\n臨尾都要咁撚中二病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0de08fed448417a2d451b3ba7d63435e9a56bf","tid":993045,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:20:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89edac1e2318a70db0884e7a0a9c46e0af924295","tid":993045,"uid":202051,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:24:25.000Z","msg":"冇戴防護架咩 磨貝殼咁多細粉就算冇重金屬都好大損害"},{"pid":"52da22070fbf8aa20d613cc46395506626f978c0","tid":993045,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89edac1e2318a70db0884e7a0a9c46e0af924295","tid":993045,"uid":202051,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:24:25.000Z","msg":"冇戴防護架咩 磨貝殼咁多細粉就算冇重金屬都好大損害"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:39:43.000Z","msg":"咪係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b1d38388ff8b6bad36089441